              target="_blank"
              >spying for Russia</a
            >. An audit of one agency exposed flaws in how it managed
            investigations, wiretaps, and forensic work (<a
              style="
                text-decoration: none;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #06266d;
                color: black;
              "
              href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-24-jul-25-spotlight-h1-3-the-audit?source=website"
              target="_blank"
              >the audit</a
            >). Zelenskyy promises the effective functioning of the agencies as
            he attempts to consolidate power within his loyalists.
          </p>
